import React from "react";
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Route, Routes } from "react-router-dom";
import { AuthProvider } from "./utils/authContext"; // Adjust path as needed
import { CreditProvider } from "./utils/creditContext"; // Adjust path as needed
import Navbar from "./components/Navbar"; // Adjust path as needed
import Login from "./components/Login"; // Adjust path as needed
import Signup from "./components/Signup"; // Adjust path as needed
import Tasks from "./components/Tasks"; // Adjust path as needed
import Home from "./components/Home"; // Adjust path as needed

function App() {
  return (
    <Router>
      <AuthProvider>
        <CreditProvider>
          <Navbar />
          <Routes>
            <Route path="/" element={<Home />} />
            <Route path="/tasks" element={<Tasks />} />
            <Route path="/login" element={<Login />} />
            <Route path="/signup" element={<Signup />} />
          </Routes>
        </CreditProvider>
      </AuthProvider>
    </Router>
  );
}

export default App;
